is the number of creatures speaking polyglot language greater than skald language?
are angels characterized by the greater average value of experience points than demons?

query.sparql: SELECT (if(?avg_ang_XP>?avg_dem_XP, 'True', 'False') as ?res) WHERE { {SELECT (AVG(?ang_XP) as ?avg_ang_XP) WHERE { ?angels <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Beast>; <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasXPValue> ?ang_XP FILTER regex(str(?angels), 'angel', 'i')}} {SELECT (AVG(?dem_XP) as ?avg_dem_XP) WHERE { ?demons <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Beast>; <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasXPValue> ?dem_XP FILTER regex(str(?demons), 'demon', 'i')}} }

question.string: do Lamia and Lilith have a common language and alignment?
do Lorelei and sirens speak the same languages?
what is the average dexterity attribute for Phoenix and Sleipnir?
what is the maximum constitution attribute for Kraken and Leviathan?
what is the minimum wisdom attribute for Gorynych and Vodyanoi?
does Kitsune or Rusalka have charisma attribute more than 20?
do both Amon and Cetus have strength attribute between 15 and 25?
does Sandman or Charon speak elder or boggarg language?

query.sparql: ASK WHERE { <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Sandman> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasLanguages> ?Sandman_lang. <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Charon> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasLanguages> ?Charon_lang FILTER((<http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#ElderL> in (?Sandman_lang) || <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#BoggargL> in (?Sandman_lang)) || (<http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#ElderL> in (?Charon_lang) || <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#BoggargL> in (?Charon_lang)))}
